# Bajaj / Hulhas Auto - Project Status & Documentation

## Overview
This project is a full-stack web application for a vehicle dealership (Bajaj). It manages inventory (bikes and scooters), promotional offers, customer leads, and an advanced admin dashboard.

## Tech Stack architecture

### Backend (`apps/backend`)
- **Framework**: NestJS (v10)
- **Database**: PostgreSQL with Prisma ORM
- **Authentication**: JWT & Passport
- **Key Modules**:
  - `Auth`: User authentication and role management (ADMIN vs USER).
  - `Products`: Inventory management, specifications (with JSON support), stock availability, pricing, and images.
  - `Offers`: Promotional campaigns, finance details (APR, tenure), and exchange offers.
  - `Leads`: Tracking customer inquiries, budgets, and sales pipeline statuses (NEW, CONTACTED, CLOSED).
  - `Settings`: Dynamic site configuration.
  - `Uploads`: File and image handling.

### Frontend (`apps/frontend`)
- **Framework**: Next.js 14.1 (App Router)
- **Styling & Animations**: Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion
- **UI Toolkit**: Radix UI (shadcn/ui), Lucide React icons
- **State & Forms**: React Hook Form, Zod validation
- **Key Sections**:
  - `Home (/)`: Client-facing landing page.
  - `Inventory (/inventory)`: Public catalog.
  - `Admin (/admin)`: Secure dashboard managing the complete backend data pipeline. Includes recent visual overhauls (cross-pattern backgrounds) and preparations for 3D model viewing.

## Current Status (Latest Enhancements)
- **Schema & Persistence**: Fully defined Data Models mapped to Postgres via Prisma. `Product` schema includes dynamic `specs`, relationships to `ProductImage`, and enums for Categories/Availability.
- **Backend Infrastructure**: Scaffolded out and configured securely with module separation and dependency injection.
- **Frontend UI & Components**: High-fidelity modern interface setup with Radix UI components (Avatars, Dialogs, Selects, Sliders, Switch, Tabs, Toasts, etc.) for a polished Admin UX.
- **Admin Panel Enhancements**: The Admin area has been upgraded structurally, emphasizing a beautiful, premium visual presentation.
